Class PCModel

java.lang.Object
model.NetworkDeviceModel
model.PCModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
NetworkDevice
public class PCModel extends NetworkDeviceModel
Represents a PC model in the network simulation. Handles its network configuration and connectivity, including ARP caching.
